response.overview: The events take place between the husband (Saleh) and his wife (Razia). They are a couple whose marriage has been long, and problems begin to creep between them, and each of them begins to blame the other. Because of their differences, their son (Suleiman) and his wife find themselves in an unenviable situation. They intervene to resolve their quarrels, and they have many comedic situations.
response.title: مني منك 2022
